				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-S%C6%A1n/Ch%C3%BAng-tinh-la-li%E1%BB%87t-d%E1%BA%A1-th%C3%A2m-minh/poem-XB_mW71WpYQ-xA8JkW2eqg">Chúng tinh la liệt dạ thâm minh - 眾星羅列夜深明</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-S%C6%A1n/author-o98HuijKnTRKdgvHyXbEYw">Hàn Sơn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Thi-Ki%C3%AAn-Ng%C3%B4/D%E1%BA%A1-nham-dao/poem-mUA-QguzchJzVyoM6Uve4g">Dạ nham dao - 夜巖謠</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Thi-Ki%C3%AAn-Ng%C3%B4/author-qmxkUt-i7s_YdIHj1-szkw">Thi Kiên Ngô</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/%C4%90%C4%83ng-H%C3%A0-B%E1%BA%AFc-th%C3%A0nh-l%C3%A2u-t%C3%A1c/poem-JCSZwbo6To-dj_2xv2MkEA">Đăng Hà Bắc thành lâu tác - 登河北城樓作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/author-9f1Hth0gmM_PXzGNXg5Fog">Vương Duy</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-Ph%C3%A1c/%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng-B%C3%A1ch-qu%C3%A1n/poem-B93-UX0IuccpTFs4Bw8cUg">Đồng Bách quán - 桐柏觀</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-Ph%C3%A1c/author-AGCqPCIFskZR14TGi3NQzg">Chu Phác</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Trung-Ng%E1%BA%A1n/H%E1%BA%A1-%C4%91%C4%83ng-c%E1%BB%B1c/poem-vnlH5urVf16jfz50t4v5ag">Hạ đăng cực - 賀登極</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Trung-Ng%E1%BA%A1n/author-n8TXz8ZnEQ2g7U6IvK74Vw">Nguyễn Trung Ngạn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-L%E1%BB%99-c%E1%BA%A9u-kh%E1%BA%A9u/poem-MdY3wD5w5oTiHWU_5wt-Sg">Khổng Lộ cẩu khẩu - 空路苟口</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-S%C6%A1n/Kim-nh%E1%BA%ADt-nham-ti%E1%BB%81n-to%E1%BA%A1/poem-O2p1xJC8k95mEZqAswT4NA">Kim nhật nham tiền toạ - 今日巖前坐</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-S%C6%A1n/author-o98HuijKnTRKdgvHyXbEYw">Hàn Sơn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C4%83ng-K%E1%BB%B7/Nham-qu%E1%BA%BF/poem-Pkj7IyPy40Bf6YUMbvEKSQ">Nham quế - 岩桂</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C4%83ng-K%E1%BB%B7/author-rrGRphgHzx_THgdF6hbcZQ">Tăng Kỷ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Ki%E1%BB%87u/Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-ho%E1%BA%A1-h%E1%BA%A1nh-Vi-T%E1%BB%B1-L%E1%BA%ADp-S%C6%A1n-trang-th%E1%BB%8B-y%E1%BA%BFn-%E1%BB%A9ng-ch%E1%BA%BF/poem-9z7tlaJ2L4laWoPZ6D-CgA">Phụng hoạ hạnh Vi Tự Lập “Sơn trang thị yến” ứng chế - 奉和幸韋嗣立山莊侍宴應制</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Ki%E1%BB%87u/author-yGOsh2Zg2gUgZ09A-P6xFA">Lý Kiệu</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Ki%C3%AAn/T%E1%BA%A9u-b%C3%BAt-t%E1%BA%A1-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ph%C3%A1c-c%C6%B0-s%C4%A9-tr%E1%BB%A5-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng/poem-6P6ZO7tZ-0vQcxK2Zd12ow">Tẩu bút tạ Vương Phác cư sĩ trụ trượng - 走筆謝王朴居士拄杖</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Ki%C3%AAn/author-wRpSKwqTcKjFpinJIe2YPg">Hoàng Đình Kiên</a>)<br></div>	</div>
